              <h3>Building Accessible Design Systems from the Ground Up</h3>
              <p>Learn how to create design systems that prioritize accessibility and ensure consistent inclusive experiences...</p>
              <div class="card-meta">
                <span class="date">March 5, 2024</span>
                <span class="read-time">10 min read</span>
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="card-link">Read More</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="blog-card">
            <div class="card-image">
              <img src="/images/Placeholder.jpg" alt="Article thumbnail" />
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
              <span class="category-tag">User Testing</span>
              <h3>Inclusive User Testing: Beyond Traditional Methods</h3>
              <p>Explore innovative approaches to user testing that include diverse abilities and perspectives...</p>
              <div class="card-meta">
                <span class="date">February 28, 2024</span>
                <span class="read-time">7 min read</span>
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="card-link">Read More</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="blog-card">
            <div class="card-image">
              <img src="/images/Placeholder.jpg" alt="Article thumbnail" />
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
              <span class="category-tag">Development</span>
              <h3>Semantic HTML: The Foundation of Accessible Web Development</h3>
              <p>Master the art of semantic markup and learn why it's crucial for creating accessible web experiences...</p>
              <div class="card-meta">
                <span class="date">February 22, 2024</span>
                <span class="read-time">5 min read</span>
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="card-link">Read More</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="blog-card">
            <div class="card-image">
              <img src="/images/Placeholder.jpg" alt="Article thumbnail" />
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
              <span class="category-tag">Legal Compliance</span>
              <h3>Accessibility Compliance: Legal Requirements and Best Practices</h3>
              <p>Navigate the complex landscape of accessibility laws and regulations across different industries...</p>
              <div class="card-meta">
                <span class="date">February 15, 2024</span>
                <span class="read-time">12 min read</span>
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="card-link">Read More</a>
            </div>
          </article>

