              <span class="category-tag">Case Study</span>
              <h3>Case Study: Transforming an E-commerce Platform for Accessibility</h3>
              <p>A detailed look at how we improved accessibility for a major retail site, with measurable results...</p>
              <div class="card-meta">
                <span class="date">February 8, 2024</span>
                <span class="read-time">15 min read</span>
